WEBVTT

00:07:30.360 --> 00:07:32.616
The FDA then allowed

00:07:32.640 --> 00:07:35.696
the company, the drug company,

00:07:35.720 --> 00:07:39.336
to test the efficacy in a clinical trial

00:07:39.360 --> 00:07:43.920
that only included
African-American subjects.

00:07:44.760 --> 00:07:46.536
It speculated

00:07:46.560 --> 00:07:52.656
that race stood in as a proxy
for some unknown genetic factor

00:07:52.680 --> 00:07:55.456
that affects heart disease

00:07:55.480 --> 00:07:58.240
or response to drugs.

00:07:59.560 --> 00:08:03.016
But think about
the dangerous message it sent,